n the city.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>EDUCATIONAL HUB</strong> - Baguio is now considered the educational center of the North, the rise in number of students taking up tertiary levels of education goes up as much as 6% annually.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>TOURISM BREAK</strong> - The cool weather of Baguio is attractive to those living in other areas of the nation as a break from the usual tropical weather, The Summer Capital of the Philippines lives up to its popularity by providing travellers and experience only Baguio can give.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>CLIMATE CHANGE</strong> - The Philippines has experienced temperature spikes brought about by climate change. Extreme weather events have also occurred. These includes deadly and damaging typhoons, floods, severe El Niño and La Niña phenomena. Baguio with its high elevation is safe from tsunamis or flooding</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2> How to Register to become a User?</h2>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nJust leave your initial information to our <a title=\"Contact Info\" href=\"http://firmdew.comli.com/?page_id=95\"><strong>Contact Form</strong></a> then will email you the instruction how to login and details you need. Feel free :)\r\n\r\n<a class=\"button\" title=\"Contact Info\" href=\"http://firmdew.comli.com/?page_id=95\">Click Here to sent your information</a>','FAQ\'s','','publish','closed','closed','','why-invest-in-baguio-city','','','2014-09-25 14:04:52','2014-09-25 14:04:52','',0,'http://firmdew.comli.com/?page_id=139',0,'page','',0),(16,1,'2014-06-29 13:33:30','2014-06-29 13:33:30','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\r\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\r\n...or something like this:\r\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\r\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://localhost/fermdew/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Transient House','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-v1','','','2014-06-29 13:33:30','2014-06-29 13:33:30','',2,'http://firmdew.comli.com/firmdew/?p=16',0,'revision','',0),(235,1,'2015-08-04 15:13:13','2015-08-04 07:13:13','','slide4_front_view','','inherit','open','open','','slide4_front_view','','','2015-08-04 15:13:13','2015-08-04 07:13:13','',234,'http://localhost/firmdew/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/slide4_front_view.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(237,1,'2015-08-04 15:38:37','2015-08-04 07:38:37','','front','','publish','closed','closed','','front','','','2015-08-04 15:38:37','2015-08-04 07:38:37','',0,'http://localhost/firmdew/?post_type=sliders&#038;p=237',0,'sliders','',0),(238,1,'2015-08-04 15:38:06','2015-08-04 07:38:06','','slide1','','inherit','open','open','','slide1','','','2015-08-04 15:38:06','2015-08-04 07:38:06','',237,'http://localhost/firmdew/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/slide1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(20,1,'2014-06-29 13:48:14','2014-06-29 13:48:14','<h2>Real Estate In Baguio</h2>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWhen it comes to investments, the real estate market is proven to be least affected by inflation rates. Despite the housing bubble that occurred a few years ago, the property sector is still a major recipient of many investments from across the planet.\r\n\r\nOne of the major countries in Asia that bring multinational companies from across the Americas and Europe is the Philippines. This archipelago has been one of the top Asian regions that promise good returns on investments, making it an excellent destination to invest your hard-earned money in. This is especially true when it comes to its real estate market.\r\n\r\nThe Philippines is made up of three major islands: Luzon, Visayas, and Mindanao. All of which have taken thousands of expatriates who have chosen this country to be their second homes in their care. And why not? Here, foreigners get to enjoy the best in life, whether you’re looking to retire, get married, open up a business or just spend an extended vacation. The country, being composed of 7,107 islands, is teeming with beautiful beaches, breath-taking mountainviews, and astounding flora and fauna. Yet it also offers modern-day luxuries, like world-class hotels, restaurants, nightclubs and entertainment centers.\r\n\r\nBut if you’re looking for a place that lets you get away from the hustle and bustle of the city life, then you have to choose Baguio City. It’s the coldest part of the country and one of the farthest holiday destinations. Yet it’s bursting with life with the many tourists that visit here once in a while. And of course, it has first-class amenities to ensure your stay will be all worthwhile.\r\n\r\nSo if you’re looking for the perfect place to settle down or retire, make your real estate investment in Baguio City. Here are some reasons to convince you why you should live and buy a house and lot in Baguio City:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Financial support for your investment. The local government and a number of property developers are offering great deals on property financing not only to the Filipinos, but also to foreigners. This means that you can easily own a house in this city.</li>\r\n	<li>Diverse array of properties to choose from. These include golf clubs, townhomes, villas, apartelles, and condominium unit in Baguio City. Thus, you’ll be able to choose your investment well.</li>\r\n	<li>Unbiased advice to expats and locals. Whether you’re setting up a business or buying a house, Baguio City is a place where help is readily available. As a result, you’ll be able to make informed decisions immediately, whether for property appraisal or estate planning.</li>\r\n	<li>Unparalleled surroundings. Baguio City is considered the “summer capital” as it is set in the mountains, providing the coolest temperature in the country all year round and the most jaw-dropping scenery. Yet it offers excellent shopping, education, health and sports facilities.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nSo if you want to invest your money and get a high return, then you should consider Baguio City immediately.','Real Estate','','publish','closed','closed','','real-estate','','','2014-09-25 12:34:53','2014-09-25 12:34:53','',0,'http://firmdew.comli.com/firmdew/?page_id=20',0,'page','',0),(23,1,'2014-06-29 13:49:32','2014-06-29 13:49:32',' ','','','publish','open','open','','23','','','2015-07-29 14:46:29','2015-07-29 06:46:29','',0,'http://firmdew.comli.com/firmdew/?p=23',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(24,1,'2014-06-29 13:49:32','2014-06-29 13:49:32',' ','','','publish','open','open','','24','','','2015-07-29 14:46:29','2015-07-29 06:46:29','',0,'http://firmdew.comli.com/firmdew/?p=24',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(25,1,'2014-06-29 13:49:12','2014-06-29 13:49:12','<span style=\"color: #000000;\">\"Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae ab illo inventore veritatis et quasi architecto beatae vitae dicta sunt explicabo. Nemo enim ipsam voluptatem quia voluptas sit aspernatur aut odit aut fugit, sed quia consequuntur magni dolores eos qui ratione voluptatem sequi nesciunt. Neque porro quisquam est, qui dolorem ipsum quia dolor sit amet, consectetur, adipisci velit, sed quia non numquam eius modi tempora incidunt ut labore et dolore magnam aliquam quaerat voluptatem. Ut enim ad minima veniam, quis nostrum exercitationem ullam corporis suscipit laboriosam, nisi ut aliquid ex e